Package: fllr
Type: Package
Title: Functional Local Linear Regression
Version: 0.0.2
Date: 2021-05-23
Author: Stanislav Nagy <nagy@karlin.mff.cuni.cz>
Maintainer: Stanislav Nagy <nagy@karlin.mff.cuni.cz>
Depends: R (>= 2.10.0), locpol
Description: Local linear smoothing for functional data and related methods. Estimation of the regression operator and the functional derivatives in scalar-on-function linear models. Uses fast implementations of the matrix operations from BLAS or LAPACK in C called from R.
